 America (TV series)|Little America]]''\n| [[Anthology series|Anthology]]/[[Comedy-drama]]\n| {{dts|January 17, 2020}}\n| {{sort|110|1 season, 8 episodes}}\n| {{sort|030|30 min.}}\n| Renewed<ref name=\"Renewed\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[Mythic Quest: Raven's Banquet]]''\n| [[Sitcom]]\n| {{dts|February 7, 2020}}\n| {{sort|109|1 season, 9 episodes}}\n| {{sort|030|30 min.}}\n| Renewed<ref>https://www.idropnews.com/news/mythic-quest-has-already-been-pegged-for-a-second-season-on-apple-tv/125919/</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" | Upcoming\n|-\n| ''Trying''<ref>{{cite web|title=Apple Unveils First British Scripted Original, Imelda Staunton & Rafe Spall Relationship Comedy \u2018Trying\u2019 \u2013 TCA|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/apple-orders-trying-imelda-staunton-rafe-spall-1202835145/|work=Deadline|date=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n| [[Television comedy|Comedy]]\n| {{dts|May 1, 2020}}\n| {{sort|108|1 season, 8 episodes}}\n| {{sort|030|30 min.}}\n| Pending\n|-\n| ''[[Central Park (TV series)|Central Park]]''<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Animated Comedy 'Central Park' From 'Bob's Burgers' Creator & Josh Gad Lands 2-Season Pickup By Apple With Star Cast|url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/central-park-animated-comedy-series-bobs-burgers-creator-josh-gad-apple-2-season-order-kristen-bell-1202336057/|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=March 12, 2018|date=March 12, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180312205041/http://deadline.com/2018/03/central-park-animated-comedy-series-bobs-burgers-creator-josh-gad-apple-2-season-order-kristen-bell-1202336057/|archive-date=March 12, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| [[Animated sitcom]]/[[Musical film|Musical]]\n| {{dts|May 29, 2020}}<ref>{{cite tweet|number=1237407880858357760|title=A musical walk in the park. Watch #CentralPark May 29 on the Apple TV app: http://apple.co/xZaTxJDS|user=AppleTV|date=March 10, 2020|accessdate=March 10, 2020}}</ref>\n| {{sort|113|1 seasons, 13 episodes}}\n| {{sort|030|30 min.}}\n| Renewed\n|